\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula
\begin{eqnarray*}
\varepsilon & \sim & N(0,\sigma_{0}^{2}I_{n}),\textrm{ so}\\
f(\varepsilon) & = & \prod_{t=1}^{n}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi\sigma^{2}}}\exp\left(-\frac{\varepsilon_{t}^{2}}{2\sigma^{2}}\right)
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

 The joint density for
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

