\[
\hat{\theta}_{FGLS}=\left(X^{\ast\prime}\left(\hat{\Sigma}_{0}^{\ast}\right)^{-1}X^{\ast}\right)^{-1}X^{\ast\prime}\left(\hat{\Sigma}_{0}^{\ast}\right)^{-1}y^{\ast}
\]

