\]

\end_inset

 or
\begin_inset Formula
\[
y=Z\delta+\varepsilon
\]

\end_inset

 where we already have that
\begin_inset Formula
\begin{eqnarray*}
\mathcal{E}(\varepsilon\varepsilon^{\prime}) & = & \Psi\\
