name "saddlepoints"
target "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saddle_point"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 may all exist.
 Supposing
\begin_inset Formula $s(\theta)$
\end_inset

 were a quadratic function of
\begin_inset Formula $\theta,$
\end_inset

 e.g.,
\begin_inset Formula
\[
s(\theta)=a+b^{\prime}\theta+\frac{1}{2}\theta^{\prime}C\theta,
\]

\end_inset

