\begin_layout Example
OLS.
 Let the d.g.p.
 be
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=\mathbf{x}_{t}^{\prime}\theta^{0}+\varepsilon_{t},\,t=1,2,...,n,\,\theta^{0}\in\Theta.$
\end_inset

