\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}_{n}=\left(\begin{array}{llll}
\boldsymbol{x}_{1} & \boldsymbol{x}_{2} & \cdots & \boldsymbol{x}_{n}\end{array}\right)^{\prime}.$
\end_inset

