\begin_inset Formula
\[
s_{\infty}(\beta)=\left(\beta^{0}-\beta\right)^{2}E\left(X^{2}\right)+\sigma_{\varepsilon}^{2}
\]

\end_inset

 A minimizer of this is clearly
\begin_inset Formula $\beta=\beta^{0}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

