\begin_inset Formula
\[
s_{\infty}(\theta)\leq s_{\infty}(\theta_{0})
\]

\end_inset

except on a set of zero probability (by assumption b of Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Consistency of ee"

\end_inset

