\begin_inset Formula $E\left(D_{\theta}\ln f(y_{t}|x_{x},\theta_{0})\right)=0$
\end_inset

.
 So, we could set
\begin_inset Formula $m_{t}(\theta)=D_{\theta}\ln f(y_{t}|x_{x},\theta)$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Newpage newpage
\end_inset


\end_layout

