\begin_inset Formula $y_{t+j}.$
\end_inset

 This is simply
\begin_inset Formula
\[
\frac{\partial Y_{t+j}}{\partial E_{t}^{\prime}}_{(1,1)}=F_{(1,1)}^{j}
\]

\end_inset

