 impact must die off.
 Otherwise a shock causes a permanent change in the mean of
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}.$
\end_inset

 Therefore, stationarity requires that
\begin_inset Formula
\[
\lim_{j\rightarrow\infty}F_{(1,1)}^{j}=0
\]

\end_inset


