\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{2},$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{0},\gamma_{1},...,\gamma_{p})$
\end_inset

 and solve for the unknowns.
 With these, the
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{j}$
\end_inset

 for
\begin_inset Formula $j>p$
\end_inset

 can be solved for recursively.
