\backslash

\end_layout

\end_inset

simplify to
\begin_inset Formula
\[
\mathbf{X}^{\prime}\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{X}^{\prime}\mathbf{X}\beta=0,
\]

\end_inset

 the usual 0LS
