\begin_layout Theorem
Under these conditions
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\parallel h^{*}-\hat{h}_{n}\parallel=0$
\end_inset

 almost surely, provided that
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}K_{n}=\infty$
\end_inset

 almost surely.

