\begin_inset Formula $n\rightarrow\infty.$
\end_inset

 This is achieved by making
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 and
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

 in equation
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "FourierForm"

\end_inset

